title: Cory Gardner says country needs time to mourn Ginsburg death 'before the politics begin'

title: Rep. Doug Collins hit for tweeting about Ginsburg's abortion stance shortly after her death
description: GOP Rep. Doug Collins, who is running for Senate in Georgia, faced backlash when he offered condolences to “30 million babies” he said died as late Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg defended abortion laws.
